# Key Findings

## Target
Metasploitable2 VM

## Scanner
OpenVAS / Greenbone Vulnerability Manager

## Findings
- Multiple critical vulnerabilities detected
- Outdated services identified
- Weak FTP service detected
- SMB exposure identified
- Insecure remote services enabled

## High Risk Services
- vsftpd 2.3.4
- Samba
- Telnet
- UnrealIRCd

## Conclusion
The target system contains intentionally vulnerable services and demonstrates the effectiveness of vulnerability assessment using OpenVAS.
